data.description: This ranch style dream home has it all AND A FINISHED BASEMENT with a 2 car garage. Nice open living room with shiplap feature wall, dining area over looks the peaceful and fully fenced backyard. Kitchen has new butcher block counter tops and shiplap backsplash. Generous sized bedrooms all located on the main level. The finished basement is the perfect game room, large office, den or theatre room and has a rock climbing wall for anyone who's a kid at heart. Large fenced in backyard is perfect for entertaining. No HOA and the home is move in ready!
